{"tid":193880,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"資深獵頭人張慧敏直言，「裸辭」是充滿怒氣和衝動的決定","createTime":"2017-04-09T14:58:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T17:45:42.000Z","uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9b845194e7db36f518f81cfd8b2977ec4b30a6f5","tid":193880,"uid":65368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"資深獵頭人張慧敏直言，「裸辭」是充滿怒氣和衝動的決定，有目標、追尋夢想的話不算裸辭。「作為一個職場專家，最蠢嘅事永遠係你發火拍枱做嘅事，過後一定會覺得自己做得不夠好。」她認為，若真的要裸辭，應先考慮幾點：一，辭職所追求的是甚麼；二，不要低估所有東西對你的影響，包括閒言閒語，三姑六婆的無謂眼光；三，預留足夠彈藥（金錢），亦要有做兼職的準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YKiFQ5B42fY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYKiFQ5B42fY&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=3fe7bd52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YKiFQ5B42fY</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你嚇左我一跳，仲以為係周綺萍黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c51e88d2aa7c5985d264bd1d77e8fcd68dcb87ac","tid":193880,"uid":78429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"發火走人果啲叫劈炮唔撈<br />\n裸辭呢啲一聽就知係有考慮過"},{"pid":"20613e824d9e567dcaaaea0adf048a6c75df282b","tid":193880,"uid":516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:03:43.000Z","msg":"佢講個三點又冇錯"},{"pid":"e9dca3c2ddf23407aacc49c27a1194b98ea420b7","tid":193880,"uid":652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:03:58.000Z","msg":"咪同周綺萍一鳩樣，屌鳩見200 份工個碩士個hr 嘛"},{"pid":"bd25eb34800920071889d005c950f68f4f70dc3c","tid":193880,"uid":43111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"係個記者定獵頭人問題，佢解釋個兩個例子，同我日常見人用好唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c39dce39ea49ef3a96bccd3c4354898e855c8be","tid":193880,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T16:40:36.000Z","msg":"陷家剷<img src=\"/assets/face